Interface JMLIterator

All Superinterfaces:
Cloneable, Iterator, JMLType, Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
JMLEnumerationToIterator
public interface JMLIterator
extends Iterator, JMLType

A combination of JMLType and java.util.Iterator. None of these support the remove operation.
